            "animation_easing": "ease",
            "item_1_title": "UK Delivery",
            "item_1_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    All <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">UK deliveries</strong> are handled by <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DPD or Royal Mail</strong> and include full tracking and delivery notifications.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Standard delivery – From £2.95\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Delivered within <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2–5 working days</strong> across all UK locations.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Next day delivery – From £4.95\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Order by <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2pm</strong>, Monday to Friday (excluding Bank Holidays), for delivery the next working day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Free next day delivery (orders over £200)\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Order by <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2pm</strong>, Monday to Friday (excluding Bank Holidays), for delivery the next working day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Delivery cut-off and processing times\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed after <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2pm</strong> will be processed the following working day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed after 2pm on Fridays or over the weekend will be dispatched the following Monday.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed on Bank Holidays or Bank Holiday weekends will be processed on the next working day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    While we always do our best to meet these timeframes, all delivery times are <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">estimates only</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame does not guarantee delivery by a specific date and accepts no liability for delays caused by courier services, weather conditions, incomplete or incorrect address details, customs, or other factors beyond our control.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Postcode exclusions\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Next Day Delivery is not available to the following locations and postcodes. For these areas, delivery will take approximately <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2–3 working days</strong>:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    ZE*, TR21–TR25, PH15–PH50, PA20–PA40, KW0–KW17, KA27–KA28, IV*, IM*, EI*, HS1–HS9, GY9–GY10, FK17–FK21, AB31–AB56.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_2_title": "Order Processing Time",
            "item_2_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed before <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">2pm</strong> (Monday to Friday) are usually dispatched the same day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed after 2pm or on <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">Bank Holidays</strong> are dispatched the next working day.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Orders placed after 2pm on Fridays or during the weekend are dispatched the following Monday.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    During busier periods, dispatch times may be slightly extended. Once your order has shipped, you will receive a <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">tracking link</strong> to monitor its progress.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_3_title": "Responsibility & Risk",
            "item_3_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    By placing an order, you acknowledge and agree that <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">ownership of the goods</strong> transfers to you once the order is delivered to the address provided at checkout. It is your responsibility to ensure someone is available to receive the delivery.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DPD</strong> is unable to deliver after multiple attempts and your parcel is returned to us, we may apply a charge for <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">re-delivery</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">Risk of loss or damage</strong> passes to you at the point of delivery. If your tracking shows that your order has been delivered but you have not received it, you must notify us within <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">72 hours</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We will support an investigation with the courier, however please note that outcomes are determined by the courier service.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame is not liable for <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">consequential loss</strong>, inconvenience, or delays during courier investigations.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_4_title": "International Delivery",
            "item_4_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    These Terms govern <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">international orders</strong> placed through Marame’s online store and are intended to provide clarity on delivery, duties, and customer responsibilities when purchasing outside of the United Kingdom.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Shipping terms\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame offers international shipping under the following delivery options:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DAP (Delivered At Place)</strong>: Duties and taxes are payable by the customer upon arrival in the destination country. Our delivery partner will contact you directly to arrange payment before releasing the goods.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    • <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DDP (Delivered Duty Paid)</strong>: Duties and taxes are included in the shipping price at checkout. No additional payment is required on delivery.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    All international orders are shipped from the <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">United Kingdom</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Excluded destinations\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We are unable to ship to the following countries and territories:\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Afghanistan, Albania, Antarctica, Argentina, Ascension Islands, Bangladesh, Belarus, Bosnia & Herzegovina, Brazil, British Indian Ocean Territory, Christmas Islands, Cocos (Keeling) Islands, Cuba, East Timor, Easter Island, Egypt, Falkland Island, French Southern Territories, Ghana, Heard/McDonald Island, India, Indonesia, Iran, Israel, Jordan, Kenya, Kiribati, Kuwait, Marshall Islands, Mexico, Micronesia, Moldova, Myanmar, Nauru, Nigeria, Niue, North Korea, Northern Mariana Islands, Norfolk Island, Occupied Palestinian Territory, Oman, Pakistan, Philippines, Pitcairn Island, Qatar, Russia, Sahara, Samoa, Sao Tome & Principe, Saudi Arabia, Serbia, Sierra Leone, Somalia, South Africa, South Georgia/Sandwich Island, Sri Lanka, St Helena, Sudan, Svalbard & Jan Mayan, Syria, Thailand, Tajikistan, Tokelau, Tonga, Tuvalu, Ukraine, US Minor Outlying Island, Venezuela, Vietnam, Wallis and Futuna Islands, Yemen.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Delivery estimates\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Estimated delivery timeframes will be provided at checkout. These are <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">estimates only</strong> and may vary due to customs processing times, carrier delays, or events beyond our control such as severe weather, industrial action, or other disruptions.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame cannot be held responsible for delays caused by external factors.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Customs duties and taxes\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    For <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DAP shipments</strong>, the customer is responsible for paying any customs duties, taxes, or handling fees required by their local authority. These charges must be settled before delivery can occur.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    For <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">DDP shipments</strong>, duties and taxes are included in the shipping price at checkout and no additional payment is required on delivery.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Returns for international orders\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    International returns are accepted within <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">14 days of delivery</strong>, provided items are unworn, unwashed, in their original condition, and with all original swing tags attached.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Delivery costs are non-refundable and returns must be sent at the customer’s expense. We recommend using a <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">tracked service</strong> to ensure your return reaches us safely.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Currency\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Where available, prices will be displayed in the customer’s local currency. If this is not available, prices will default to <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">GBP (£)</strong>.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n    Liability for delays and losses\n  </strong>\n  <br>\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    While we work closely with our delivery partners to ensure smooth shipping, Marame is not responsible for delays caused by customs clearance procedures, incorrect delivery information provided at checkout, weather conditions, or other unforeseen logistical disruptions beyond our control.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_5_title": "Faulty or Incorrect Items",
            "item_5_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If you receive a <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">faulty or incorrect item</strong>, please contact us within <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">48 hours of delivery</strong>, including details of the issue and supporting images where possible.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We will assess the issue and, where appropriate, offer a <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">repair, replacement, or refund</strong> in accordance with your statutory rights.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_6_title": "Damaged or Missing Items",
            "item_6_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We take great care to ensure all orders are packed to a high standard before leaving our warehouse. However, on rare occasions, items may be <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">damaged or go missing</strong> during transit.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If your order arrives damaged, incomplete, or with items missing, please contact us within \n    <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">48 hours of delivery</strong> \n    at <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">help@marame.com</strong>, including your order number and clear photographs of the packaging and affected item(s).\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Once reviewed, we will advise on the next steps, which may include a \n    <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">replacement, exchange, or refund</strong>, \n    depending on the nature of the issue and stock availability.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Please note that we are unable to accept responsibility for damage reported outside of this timeframe or where supporting evidence is not provided, as this limits our ability to raise a claim with the courier.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_7_title": "Incorrect Shipping Addresses",
            "item_7_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We take great care to ensure all orders are packed to a high standard before leaving our warehouse. However, on rare occasions, items may be <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">damaged or go missing</strong> during transit.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If your order arrives damaged, incomplete, or with items missing, please contact us within \n    <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">48 hours of delivery</strong> \n    at <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">help@marame.com</strong>, including your order number and clear photographs of the packaging and affected item(s).\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Once reviewed, we will advise on the next steps, which may include a \n    <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">replacement, exchange, or refund</strong>, \n    depending on the nature of the issue and stock availability.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Please note that we are unable to accept responsibility for damage reported outside of this timeframe or where supporting evidence is not provided, as this limits our ability to raise a claim with the courier.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_8_title": "Failed Delivery Attempts",
            "item_8_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Please ensure that all <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">delivery details</strong> are correct at checkout. Once an order has been placed, we are unable to guarantee that address changes can be made before dispatch.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame cannot accept responsibility for <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">delays, failed deliveries, or parcels returned to sender</strong> due to incorrect or incomplete address information provided at checkout.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If a parcel is returned to us as undeliverable, we will contact you to arrange <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">redelivery</strong>. Additional delivery charges may apply.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_9_title": "Tracking & Delivery Confirmation",
            "item_9_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Once your order has been dispatched, you will receive a <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">confirmation email</strong> containing your tracking details. Please allow up to <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">24 hours</strong> for tracking information to update after dispatch.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    In some cases, tracking may not show movement immediately or may update in batches. This does not necessarily indicate an issue with your delivery.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If your tracking shows as <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">delivered</strong> but you have not received your parcel, please check with neighbours, building management, or any designated safe place before contacting us.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_10_title": "Split Shipments",
            "item_10_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    In some cases, orders containing <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">multiple items</strong> may be shipped in more than one parcel. If this happens, you will receive <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">separate tracking details</strong> for each shipment.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If part of your order arrives before the rest, please allow <strong style=\"text-transform:none !important; font-size:inherit;\">additional time</strong> for the remaining items to arrive before contacting us.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
